@@eThe Peoples of the Realm@@N

Many races inhabit the world of Ack!, each with their own strengths,
traditions, and histories.

From the stalwart humans who build empires, to the ancient elves who
guard the forests, to the stout dwarves who delve deep beneath the
mountains -- every race has carved its place in the tapestry of the world.

Some races are known for their martial prowess, others for their mastery
of the arcane arts. A wise adventurer studies the strengths and customs
of all peoples, for knowledge is as sharp a weapon as any blade.

Use @@yhelp race@@N in-game for mechanical details on playable races.

